summary: Embercleave bootc smoke test
description: |
  Asserts (inside the booted VM) that the host pivoted to the embercleave
  bootc image, swarm has linger enabled, the bus socket directory was
  created with correct ownership by tmpfiles.d, and embercleave-mgr.service
  came up under swarm's user-mode systemd.
test: ./test.sh
duration: 5m
tier: smoke
